      • ARE_DEBUG_LOG_ENABLED

        public static boolean ARE_DEBUG_LOG_ENABLED
        A flag which indicates whether the hereby SmartThreadPoolExecutor internal logs should be enabled. Logs will report execution durations statistics. The default value is false.
        See Also:
        getExecutionDurationSumInNanoseconds()

        public long getExecutionDurationSumInNanoseconds()
        Available for statistics.

        Warning: this method will return valid data only if ARE_DEBUG_LOG_ENABLED is set to true.
